Description.Text: This elegant European-style hotel, is known for providing the ultimate in personalized service and offers guestrooms and suites, some with glass enclosed indoor terraces and outdoor balconies. (0606/CH)

On a quiet tree-lined street in the heart of Manhattan, the hotel is nestled among genteel residences on East 64th Street between Park & Madison Avenues. This charming boutique hotel is just a stroll away from Central Park, Madison Avenue shopping, museums, and galleries.
Newly renovated and elegantly furnished guestrooms include Asian silk bedspreads and draperies, Belgian linens, 42-inch plasma or LCD flat screen televisions, carpeting and wallpaper.

The French restaurant is an elegant gold domed room with Murano glass and brass chandeliers, combining a touch of Europe and Asia. The chiffon colored walls with murals of pagodas and faux conservatory windows create a serene and soothing mood. And the bar is famous for its exotic atmosphere and eclectic d√©cor.
